HR Executive required for Irish owned HR Consultancy in Dubai
ONLY APPLY WITH REQUESTED INFORMATION BELOW OTHERWISE YOUR APPLICATION NOT ACCEPTED
a) Please advise what sectors you can source for b) please advise what countries and professionals you can source c) what are your interview / testing techniques d) you have access to candidates database e) your availability on freelance basis, please advise You should be sharp, attention to detail, professional, and well experienced . Please forward feedback to the above by email and forward your cv to marie@emiratesint.com Tel Marie 00971555410096
Requirements
smart approach to selecting candidates access to candidates locally and internationally attention to detail a must
